<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Hotel Notifications Center</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@200..800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#135bec",
                        "royal-blue": "#1052D5",
                        "background-light": "#f6f6f8",
                        "background-dark": "#101622",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Manrope"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
        body {
          min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
        }
        .glass-nav {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
    </style>
<style>
    body {
      min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
    }
  </style>
  </head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 antialiased">
<div class="flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col max-w-md mx-auto relative pb-24 shadow-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
<header class="sticky top-0 z-10 bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-md px-6 pt-12 pb-4">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
<button class="flex items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
</button>
<div class="flex-1 text-center">
<span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary opacity-70">Roomie Guest</span>
</div>
<div class="size-10"></div>
</div>
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Notifications</h1>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-4 space-y-4 pt-2">
<div class="px-2">
<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Today</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
<div class="shrink-0">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-cover bg-center border-2 border-primary/10" data-alt="Platter of fresh gourmet seafood dinner" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB2R6mwAvGQ7KweUdAA4d7_OZpDZ_xjH1kkE1kGRrf34135oxdDXLJTQHBfh8z2gd3L2yA5KSbWsbdoCK7f2Gj1snVH0vFy7uOZcZSXLhhj3W4NLcFhrQMHqlz44VZLLKV4biQKQP7AGHrPpOnSwVb441una3RkAhqnnntRaPtDxVfbA0aVWTPjW6xCRyczK1IbWrnuAfqhKM39RuHZERF1fromoGzWkQ39BoxatKO8MZccqciQ5O1NXrtFFbFuDNBEhpgzLCfRUCH-')"></div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col flex-1 gap-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
<span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Dining</span>
<span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-medium">Just now</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-base leading-tight">Seafood Special</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Fresh seafood has just arrived! Try our new ocean-to-table dishes today.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
<div class="shrink-0">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-cover bg-center border-2 border-primary/10" data-alt="Relaxing spa setting with massage oils" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCRlcq2LC-VSLTRpFH6GcTGDLlukADE4Yc4MN5Wg5ERSQuL34uPM2MWz-mRca-LZhImmo7u1VZLQEmUkGcA68ZCL8kSOTEDeOeG8M9UIsSpFH2jOLVurqwUvq6DMpBfLrfWzFu6GtUTVJ_PR1Jy6BzMp8casE7LJ3htsFSsU-084igpZiuSzP1F3rJfL-n_F1xg0pRj4F3r8xHJwO1MCuDeI19T3hfN_6flv6vwyj-ENJpsFLJKcGMmAgglRM2cHQXAGT-GTaL46nf_')"></div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col flex-1 gap-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
<span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Wellness</span>
<span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-medium">2h ago</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-base leading-tight">New Spa Services</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Experience bliss with our new Thai massage techniques now available at the Spa.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="px-2 pt-2">
<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Yesterday</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 opacity-90">
<div class="shrink-0">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-cover bg-center border-2 border-primary/10" data-alt="High quality ribeye steak on a plate" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDNjqbWUSXdBgpfh2HwAHcC-CxRXDcXgwuiTHvILrXwfrLkGmkGWxtKGkzWELF6a6LwKzIDO9HRaWFHa5U0EfD6z0CMezGhS9uIxSXVmZirc-zJZV60O4PFEbPne4qLlIHE8MxBHj7xjiTUAolB9DKYRttsN8N9uyQ2g7x41YFJ4hFnQbHCpBbRY8mXnGgmqBRFLZnE7tX1KgwjFw_sVUT5oVTs-eLjoAhndVMYdL2DhNr0No92bChYBJYfSp9WVhh7RzyMWH7PpINF')"></div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col flex-1 gap-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
<span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Dining Offer</span>
<span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-medium">1d ago</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-base leading-tight">Meat Lover's Night</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Special discount on meat dishes today. We highly recommend our Signature Ribeye Steak.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 opacity-90">
<div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center size-14 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">star_rate</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col flex-1 gap-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
<span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Concierge</span>
<span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-medium">1d ago</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-base leading-tight">Feedback Request</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">How was your stay? Share your experience with us.</p>
</div>
</div>
</main>
<div class="fixed bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[90%] max-w-[380px] z-50">
<nav class="glass-nav rounded-full px-6 py-3 flex items-center justify-between shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]">
<a class="flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500 hover:text-royal-blue transition-colors group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">home</span>
<span class="text-[10px] font-medium">Home</span>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-royal-blue relative" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1">room_service</span>
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold">Services</span>
<div class="absolute -bottom-1.5 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-royal-blue"></div>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500 hover:text-royal-blue transition-colors group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">shopping_bag</span>
<span class="text-[10px] font-medium">Orders</span>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500 hover:text-royal-blue transition-colors group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">account_circle</span>
<span class="text-[10px] font-medium">Account</span>
</a>
</nav>
</div>
</div>

</body></html>